NOTE on content (Markdown files under luxun-perspective/):

The Lu Xun corpus excerpts referenced are from works in the public domain
(Lu Xun, 1881-1936). The distilled framework, mental models, and editorial
text in this repository are released under the same MIT License above.

This skill represents an interpretive framework based on Lu Xun's published
corpus. It is not, and does not claim to be, Lu Xun himself.
